an interface that any PlotFit needs to use to get the curve for the plot fit. The algorithm takes an XYDataSource and comes up with a plot fit formula. Then, using this formula, it must return a y for any x supplied. The PlotFit class is responsible for querying the PlotFitAlgorithm for the data points in order to get the curve to display.
